00:04:23.738 --> 00:04:26.282
''down by the wharf riverside district.

00:04:26.366 --> 00:04:27.741
''Let's go see him tonight.

00:04:27.826 --> 00:04:29.076
''I think you'll really like him.''

00:04:29.160 --> 00:04:33.455
<i>So that night, I remember,</i>
<i>we pull up...</i>

00:04:33.581 --> 00:04:36.709
<i>away in this kinda isolated</i>
<i>part of Detroit</i>

00:04:36.793 --> 00:04:38.836
<i>right on the side of the Detroit River,</i>

00:04:38.920 --> 00:04:42.756
<i>and you could see the mist in the air</i>
<i>coming off the river. We could feel it.</i>

00:04:42.841 --> 00:04:46.552
