it's all full of smoke,

00:05:00.650 --> 00:05:02.276
so there's a mist inside there.

00:05:02.694 --> 00:05:05.904
<i>(Mike Theodore) Boom, hey, you know,</i>
<i>it's a wall of smoke.</i>

00:05:06.865 --> 00:05:10.576
<i>Beer all over the place. Peanut shells.</i>
<i>It was just a mess.</i>

00:05:10.660 --> 00:05:14.663
