01:01:39.963 --> 01:01:42.256
<i>(Segerman) So I told him,</i>
<i>''You're bigger than Elvis,''</i>

01:01:42.298 --> 01:01:43.882
<i>and he said, ''What do you mean?''</i>

01:01:43.967 --> 01:01:47.636
<i>I said, ''In South Africa you are</i>
