01:01:59.107 --> 01:02:01.942
<i>(Emmerson)</i>
<i>He's working his ass off in Woodbridge.</i>

01:02:01.985 --> 01:02:05.654
One day, be brought this picture
of himself on a milk carton.

01:02:05.739 --> 01:02:07.823
(chuckles)

01:02:07.949 --> 01:02:12.619
And he'd say, ''Emmerson, look at this.
You know, they're looking for me.''

01:02:14.414 --> 01:02:18.000
I said,
''Really? Why is that, Rodriguez?''

01:02:18.918 --> 01:02:22.087
<i>Next day he says,</i>
<i>''Emmerson, I gotta go on tour.''</i>

01:02:22.672 --> 01:02:25.007
<i>I said, ''Come on, Rodriguez,</i>
<i>are you serious?''</i>

01:02:25.133 --> 01:02:26.967
<i>(Rian Malan) Because I'm a journalist,</i>
<i>I doubted it.</i>

01:02:27.010 --> 01:02:29.928
<i>That sort of thing does not happen</i>
<i>in the rational universe.</i>

01:02:30.013 --> 01:02:32.848
<i>It does not happen.</i>
<i>It's against the laws of God and nature.</i>

01:02:32.974 --> 01:02:35.309
<i>This guy is coming to tour here,</i>
<i>he must be an imposter.</i>

01:02:35.351 --> 01:02:38.145
It's a clever public relations scam.

01:02:38.188 --> 01:02:41.815
