01:06:45.309 --> 01:06:47.477
of the songs that we've got

01:06:47.520 --> 01:06:48.937
in the studio here in Cape Town

01:06:49.022 --> 01:06:52.441
on the day that he came
from the airport, when he arrived,

01:06:52.483 --> 01:06:56.153
and we were actually in the middle
of a song when he walked in

01:06:56.279 --> 01:06:58.947
and just took over the microphone
and finished the song.

01:06:59.032 --> 01:07:01.450
We switched off the CD player

01:07:01.492 --> 01:07:04.286
and it was, like, completely seamless.

01:07:04.328 --> 01:07:05.704
<i>Completely seamless.</i>

01:07:05.788 --> 01:07:07.956
<i>I mean, ''OK, this is the guy.''</i>

01:07:08.041 --> 01:07:09.791
<i>I think we all knew this is</i>

01:07:09.834 --> 01:07:11.960
<i>gonna be something really special.</i>

01:07:29.979 --> 01:07:32.647
<i>Thank you, Cape Town. Thank you.</i>

01:07:34.525 --> 01:07:35.567
<i>(Regan) When we, uh...</i>

01:07:35.651 --> 01:07:36.735
<i>initially got on a plane,</i>

01:07:36.819 --> 01:07:38.820
<i>I thought maybe there'd be, hopefully,</i>

01:07:38.863 --> 01:07:41.073
<i>20 people in the audience.</i>

