<i>at that place</i>

01:12:28.861 --> 01:12:31.237
<i>he'd tried to find his whole life.</i>

01:12:31.322 --> 01:12:33.656
<i>(Segerman) Home is acceptance.</i>

01:12:34.075 --> 01:12:37.577
<i>Here's a guy who'd lived somewhere else,</i>
<i>on the other side of the earth,</i>

01:12:37.661 --> 01:12:40.872
<i>and it was almost as if</i>
<i>he had found his home.</i>

01:12:40.915 --> 01:12:42.916
<i>(Bartholomew-Strydom)</i>
<i>And I looked around at all these people</i>

01:12:43.000 --> 01:12:46.669
<i>and I thought, ''This is</i>
<i>a once-in-a-lifetime experience.</i>

01:12:46.754 --> 01:12:49.798
<i>''This is never going to happen again.''</i>

