<i>(Rodriguez) Oh, they were so sweet.</i>

01:15:01.222 --> 01:15:03.389
<i>I didn't believe it.</i>

01:15:03.474 --> 01:15:06.226
<i>And I still don't, but the thing is...</i>

01:15:06.310 --> 01:15:11.981
So when I went on stage
5,000 seats all set up,

01:15:12.024 --> 01:15:14.359
white seats, and the thing is...

01:15:14.693 --> 01:15:17.278
And I said, ''This is...''

01:15:18.572 --> 01:15:23.201
<i>So when I played a show, they jumped</i>
<i>out of their seats and rushed the stage.</i>

01:15:24.912 --> 01:15:29.082
<i>South Africa made me feel like</i>
<i>more than a prince.</i>

01:15:29.750 --> 01:15:33.044
<i>(Eva) And then signing the autographs</i>
<i>for, like, a couple of hours.</i>

01:15:33.087 --> 01:15:37.298
<i>I mean, just the line of people</i>
<i>bringing their guitars to be signed,</i>

01:15:37.383 --> 01:15:39.425
<i>bringing their CDs and...</i>

01:15:39.510 --> 01:15:40.969
<i>(Regan) The most amazing thing I'd seen</i>

01:15:41.053 --> 01:15:43.930
<i>was the man with his tattoo</i>
<i>of the</i> Cold Fact.

01:15:44.014 --> 01:15:48.101
<i>He was a Rodriguez impersonator.</i>
<i>That just stoked my fire.</i>

01:15:48.143 --> 01:15:51.229
<i>I was like,</i>
<i>''Man, that is just too crazy.''</i>

