OK, will you?

01:16:06.161 --> 01:16:07.620
(all laughing)

01:16:07.746 --> 01:16:11.958
American singer Rodriguez
is certainly alive and well

01:16:12.001 --> 01:16:14.335
and with us in the Front Row tonight.
Welcome.

01:16:14.461 --> 01:16:15.920
Very kind. How are you?

